Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:48.98,sign_3960_43_Film_Director_To,Headline sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz41\fax0.41\b0\pos(317,246)}Police believe that Komatsu and an accomplice attempted to slice open\Nthe stomach of movie producer Jubei Honda (52). Mr. Honda is in\N critical condition, but Mr. Komatsu denies the allegations stating he does\N not recall what happened.\N\NMr. Komatsu and Mr. Honda were reportedly having disagreements\N over finances for their newest movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:52.92,main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be your first time \Nonscreen together in sixteen years, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.58,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that big a deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.67,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. To be honest, we kind of saw this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.07,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We are so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:05.28,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We can actually visit our daughter's \Nculture festival, thanks to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:08.82,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We were onscreen together sixteen years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.29,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but we've never been to her cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.02,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't exactly been the most... \Npresent of parents for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.43,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to improvise a kettle \Nstand from pegs like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.07,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I do impress myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.46,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's to the culture \Nfestival being a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.54,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.02,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.35,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to need to attract an \Naudience for today's screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.58,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely want lots of people to watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:00.81,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.98,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but our primary objective \Ntoday is to score preorders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.13,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,for the DVD release after \Nthe screening today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.23,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.06,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why we need an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:12.14,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,First, since it's summer, we'll need to \Nmake sure our auditorium is nice and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.66,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:17.02,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear the HVAC club are \Nlackeys of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. I've got \Nwhat I need to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.86,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But more important than even that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.42,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,is the involvement of the popular \Namateur model Tsubame Mizusaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.63,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and how much we can \Nput her out in front of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.14,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.75,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sounds like the anime \Nwould be playing second fiddle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.33,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,to Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.89,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.68,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We're using you along with \Nair-conditioning to get people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.67,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,to pay attention to the anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.68,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,not the other way around. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.60,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.85,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win over the people who \Ncame to see you with the anime's quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.91,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Which we can't do if they won't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:59.07,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And if the short is good enough, \Nthey're bound to preorder the DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.52,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of extra responsibility..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:05.43,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a big spotlight that'll \Nallow us to draw plenty of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.74,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We need to use that to our \Nadvantage as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.27,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we like it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:14.46,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,if it benefits our production situation \Nin the long run, we need to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.31,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda worried
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.82,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,my parents might find out if \NI draw too much attention, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.55,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, if your parents find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.84,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asakusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.22,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding your chopsticks kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.37,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You can actually grab stuff like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.35,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be our poster girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.70,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,My parents found out I didn't go home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.44,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.42,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If they knew I was working \Non the culture festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.78,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,they'd want to know specifics...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:52.24,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,And they just told me... that they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.83,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:06:00.33,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But if they find out, you won't be \Nable to make anime anymore, Mizusaki!
