Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.21,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Keep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.56,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Your
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.13,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Hands
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.51,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:19.50,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:27.71,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken,Title zoom in/Scroll out,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.48,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this, Mizusaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:48.45,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if they find out anymore! \NMy family situation can suck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.31,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If they're coming, then bring 'em on!\N I'll give them a real eyeful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.25,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I can't bring in \Na crowd for this screening,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.46,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,we're at a dead end anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.37,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! You'll have our \Nfull support as backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.28,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,For once, we're gonna \Ntackle things with spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:04.37,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit, spirit, spirit, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:08.44,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've already lost the chance \Nto form a line, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.42,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's like everyone's putting \Non a spirited show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.42,main,Carbogirls,0000,0000,0000,,Our electromagnetic amoeba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.42,sign_11759_124_Electro_magnetic,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Electro-\Nmagnetic\N Amoeba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.42,sign_11759_125_Accessibility_Re,Wheelchair sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz60\move(500,200,465,155)}Accessibility \N{\c&H1F1E1E&}Research Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.07,sign_11807_126_Pi_Research_Club,Fan sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pi Research Club \N~The Beauty of Pi~ \N{\fs20\fnComic Sans MS}Pi Is Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.22,sign_11826_127_Rap_Club,Banner sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-84.81\pos(354,36)}Rap Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.22,sign_11826_128_Rakuda,Other banner sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-89.02\pos(270,113)\fax-0.27}Rakuda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.84,main,Rap Club,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the best there is! No. 1 in the biz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:15.97,sign_11874_130_Short_Wave_Radio,Fan sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shortwave Radio Research Club!\N{\fnComic Sans MS\fs16}Shortwave radio tournament coming up on the East Tower roof
