Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.51,sign_11893_132_Shaved_Ice_Club,Blue Banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.5\pos(62,34)}Shaved {\c&HC34D28&}Ice {\c&H393940&}Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.51,main,Captive Eater,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot! That radish is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.51,top,Shaved Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone want some shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.28,sign_11953_135_Shingeki_Theater,Fan sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shingeki Theater Research Club \N{\fs20\c&H174555&\fnComic Sans MS\3c&H6E9EB1&} We will be performing in Auditorium 3!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.18,sign_11977_136_Presented_by_the,Eizoken flier sign,0000,0000,0000,,Presented by the Robot Study Club Featuring the Eizouken\N{\fs20\fnVerdana\c&HFFFEFD&\3c&HBDA19D&}SHIBA8 {\c&H7975D2&\3c&HFFFFFF&}VS {\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&H969EDC&}The Pistol Crabtle\N{\fs14\c&H8CBE9A&\3c&HFFFFFE&}The Great Shibahama Festival!\N{\fs10\c&H887EB8&}Including an appearance by the famous model\N{\fs30\c&HFBC756&}Tsubame Mizusaki\N\N{\fs20\c&H5F605E&}Join us!\N\N\N{\fs14}Something will happen\Nin Shibahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.28,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're the eizouken! Please check us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.13,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki has worked on an anime—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:26.73,top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please come by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.27,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've got anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:31.03,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki will be appearing at—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:35.41,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even the people who'd come to see \Nyou won't notice us at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.87,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.83,sign_12427_145_Tsubame_Mizusaki,Robot Box signs,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.85,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The robot club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.78,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,The prep took longer than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:53.88,sign_12701_147_Tsubame_Mizusaki,Banner sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki! We're Launching a Rocket Before the Robot Anime Screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.04,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.88,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.60,main,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Count down along with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.72,main,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Ten! Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.27,main,Eizouken,0000,0000,0000,,Eight! Seven! Six! Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.85,sign_12701_147_Tsubame_Mizusaki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10}Tsubame Mizusaki! We're Launching a Rocket Before the Robot Anime Screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.11,main,Eizouken,0000,0000,0000,,Four! Three! Two! One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.11,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.44,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,A robot anime featuring Tsubame Mizusaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.62,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,will be screening in Auditorium No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.70,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I made an anime! Come check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.21,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be greeting the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.98,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.98,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,It's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.22,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.97,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.22,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Dang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.84,main,Rap Club,0000,0000,0000,,Man, celebs have it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.40,main,Other clubs,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was a ban on megaphones?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.20,sign_13831_166_Three_Star_Resta,Other clubs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Three-Star\NRestaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.68,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and cool inside! Care to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.68,top,Other clubs,0000,0000,0000,,So she gets away with it because she's famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.18,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave this to Mizusaki \Nand the robot club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.27,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We need to cover the rest of the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.60,main,Other two,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.57,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,What about twenty-two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:04.08,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is that number your idea of a joke? \NBecause I'm not here for comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.97,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:06.73,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.54,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.57,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Twenty-one suit you better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.85,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.54,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.98,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:16.88,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.95,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I said sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.51,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,You dirty, rotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.52,sign_14986_183_Auditorium_1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Auditorium 1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:38.99,sign_15076_184_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for every degree°
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.82,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a deal, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.77,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,President, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.16,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,It's ecologically criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.42,main,HVAC Club,0000,0000,0000,,And if the student council \Nfinds out, we'll be in huge trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.99,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,You're all guilty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.82,main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,If these pictures get out, we're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.25,main,Club,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! She's a monster! A devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.01,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Autographs will be available \Nat the screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.96,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,This is a handshake-only promotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.98,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Head to the auditorium if you want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.98,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't crowd together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.98,top,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.98,main,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed into school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.22,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,The use of megaphones and aerial \Naccoutrements is forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.54,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,What were you going to do if you \Nhit someone with that rocket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.07,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki of the eizouken, you're under\N arrest as the ringleader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.82,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,This is a promotion by the robot club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.73,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility lies with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.03,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, head on over to \NAuditorium No. 1 and shake hands with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.23,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:25.56,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Kanamori gave the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.65,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to protect you, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.21,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.08,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Anything for the robot anime's screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.97,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mizusaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.58,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.80,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the robot club, \Nbut I don't see any cardboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:48.57,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.81,italics,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki, excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.94,italics,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Now you just need to make \Nit to the auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.23,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Is this gonna work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.82,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going ahead. I'll direct you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.59,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in a cardboard robot is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for the security club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.83,italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:16.33,sign_17475_221_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz66.6\fax-0.08\pos(145,312)}Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:16.33,sign_17475_222_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz67.31\fax-0.22\pos(199,188)}Woodworking\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:16.33,sign_17475_223_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz26.57\fax-0.5\pos(543,139)\fay-.04}Karaage\NRamen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.14,italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Head down those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:26.09,sign_17674_222_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.47,italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.83,italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Keep going, and then head \Ninto the hall on your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.14,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.06,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.60,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Get that one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.10,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We've caught a robot we believe to be Mizusaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.44,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We've also caught one of the Mizusaki robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.44,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.44,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We've spotted a crowd of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.10,italics,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We'll move to apprehend them—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.10,italics,Security,0000,0000,0000,,We've restrained one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.82,italicstop,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Got another one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.49,italics,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Should we pursue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.45,main,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,How many people are even in the eizouken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.90,main,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.31,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:53.50,sign_18430_238_Japanese_Marchin,Box Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese Marching Band Study Group\N\N{\fs18\c&H21302C&\3c&HEFEAE0&}The {\c&H413CD0&}robot anime {\c&H21302C&}will\Nbe screening in Auditorium No. 1!\NThe famous {\c&HFC8909&}Tsubame\N Mizusaki {\c&H21302C&}will be there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:53.50,main,Band,0000,0000,0000,,Paper robot costumes are available \Nto anyone who wants one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:58.37,main,Band,0000,0000,0000,,Make it to Auditorium No. 1 \Nin your robot cosplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:02.21,main,Band,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll receive some \Nspecial Tsubame merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.22,sign_18755_242_Presented_by_the,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Presented by the Robot Study Club Featuring the Eizouken\N{\fs20\fnVerdana\c&HB8B7B7&\3c&H9A564D&}SHIBA8 {\3c&HB8B7B7&\c&H58509F&}VS {\c&HB8B7B7&\3c&H625EA3&}The Pistol Crabtle\N{\fs14\3c&HB8B7B7&\c&H63856D&}The Great Shibahama Festival!\N{\fs10\c&H4A4784&}Including an appearance by the famous model\N{\fs30\c&HB58D4E&}Tsubame Mizusaki\N\N{\fs20\c&H3F3E3A&}will be there!\N\N\N{\fs14}Something will happen\Nin Shibahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.22,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, it takes place at the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.26,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. With a few alterations, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:13.93,sign_18803_244_Cardboard_Robot_,Banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-34\fax0.45\pos(196,63)\fay.02}Cardboard Robot Distribution
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.83,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.41,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,And to think a girl like her \Nis making a robot anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.97,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.93,sign_18803_245_Tsubame_Mizusaki,Banner,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.93,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks for your interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.05,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.40,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,This is oppression by the majority—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.40,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Get those boxes off them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.66,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.47,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them might not be students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.43,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.61,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting away! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:32.95,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,My soul, dadada! A body of iron, dadada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:39.17,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,An invincible body with a steel \Nheart fighting to the end, dadada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.67,top,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Dun dun dun dun, \Nmachines have no tears to shed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:43.67,main,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Ono... he's powering up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.93,top,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,But you can see the passion \Nwelling up inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.07,main,Kumajima,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deal with them later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.93,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.72,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.30,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.47,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.73,sign_19960_269_Robot_anime_scre,Ono back sign,0000,0000,0000,,Robot anime screening in Auditorium No. 1!\N With Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.98,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, an anime screening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.80,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:56.74,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.81,sign_20062_273_Zipline,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Zip Line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.54,sign_20411_277_Zipline,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(240,170,285,170)}Z       {\3c&HEAEFEC&}I       {\3c&HE1E4BB&}P       {\3c&HEAEDEC&}L         {\3c&HEEEAAA&}I        {\3c&HEFF2F1&}NE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.61,main,Zipline Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.54,main,Zipline Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.67,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Switch: Super Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.17,main,Zipline Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Easy does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:30.45,sign_20780_278_Robot_anime_scre,Pink Banner Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Robot anime screening featuring Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.48,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.43,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.18,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Holy moly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.14,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.16,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna check your show out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.32,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:01.33,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.01,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.15,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Asakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.18,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's still passing out \Nfliers near the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.00,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She should be on her way back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.18,main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki! We need you \Nstanding by at stage left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.43,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,I did it... I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.09,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:17.68,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.06,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The show's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.37,sign_11977_136_Presented_by_the,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Presented by the Robot Study Club Featuring the Eizouken\N{\fs20\fnVerdana\c&HFFFEFD&\3c&HCD7C70&}SHIBA8 {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H836BEE&}VS {\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&H97A0E0&}The Pistol Crabtle\N{\fs14\3c&HFFFFFE&\c&H8EB099&}The Great Shibahama Festival!\N{\fs10\c&H887EB8&}Including an appearance by the famous model\N{\fs30\c&HFBC756&}Tsubame Mizusaki\N\N{\fs20\c&H5F605E&}will be there!\N\N\N{\fs14}Something will happen\Nin Shibahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.16,main,MIBS,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.19,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Men in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.23,main,MIBs,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.07,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.42,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,The robot club has holed up\N inside Auditorium No. 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.78,main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Should we breach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.16,main,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take them in if \Nthey're inside the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.29,main,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,Nail them as soon as they set foot outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.79,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! Oh crap! Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.11,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I just handed a flier to some men \Nin black and Mizusaki's parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.63,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.27,main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:03.13,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,The robot study club will now \Nbegin the screening of its anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.73,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,This should be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.25,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.77,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.63,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:19.79,main,MIBS,0000,0000,0000,,We're so sorry. We tried to stop her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.04,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.25,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It was my idea. I wanted to get \NTsubame's mind off of anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.95,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted her to be an actress, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.23,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I am really excited for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.36,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.48,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.81,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.92,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's really Shibahama! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.88,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.34,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Why so much crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.41,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.77,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Vibrations have been detected \Nin the underground pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.30,italics,Goto,0000,0000,0000,,A monster resembling a crab has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.78,italics,Goto,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, a monster resembling \Na crab has appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.33,main,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up... Easy does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.79,sign_9995_143_Preparing_Launch,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(334,194)\frz-11.11\fax0.1\fay-.009\fad(1,435)}Preparing Launch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.58,sign_9995_143_Preparing_Launch,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-12.5\fax0.1\fay-.009\pos(353,114)\fs40\fad(435,1)\fscx200\fscy200\c&HA3FEFD&}Launching
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.63,main,Seki,0000,0000,0000,,Head directly to the subterranean waterway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:59.09,italics,Goto,0000,0000,0000,,The target is on a slow and steady \Ncourse through the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.93,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Recoil starter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.46,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That running...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.55,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsubame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.19,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,A cooling fan is down, and the movement \Nsoftware isn't coming online!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.71,main,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Manual control?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:16.53,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You remember how Tsubame's \Nalways been good at dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.73,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She'd mimic what she saw on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:22.55,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She used to imitate \Nhow her grandma moved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.50,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And that bit before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.39,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She was always analyzing and \Nrepeating things she saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.06,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.66,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.90,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She started having more fun \Nrecreating the movements
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.93,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,she saw with art, rather than with her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.96,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think her real talent is her eye for detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.72,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And even without the help of their parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.85,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kids will still grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.94,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's real ingenuity to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.60,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I've been on her case about \Nbecoming an actress, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.61,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame is already a fine performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.61,sign_29758_353_Missing_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-6.34\fax0.08\pos(248,213)\fad(1,611)\t(2592,3909,\3c&H2E260C&)}Sponsor\N{\fs12}Robot Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.55,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:52.55,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.90,sign_30058_356_Tsubame_Mizusaki,Banner sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-86.4\fax0.32\fscx105\pos(109,193)}Tsubame Mizusaki Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.90,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Preorder your DVD now and you'll get a bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:02.15,sign_30173_358_Candid_Photos_of,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1\move(433,20,433,70,1,130)\fscx105}Candid Photos{\u0} of Animator {\b1\c&H5239C3&}Tsubame Mizusaki{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.85,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.15,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get that bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.13,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Please line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.80,top,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,An invincible body and a steel heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.16,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get in line, you don't get the bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.92,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.98,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.93,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming by!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.68,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:22.42,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Head out the back and grab \Nus some lunch, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.46,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.46,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We've got plenty to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.68,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And if you preorder now, you can get an \Nautographed picture of Tsubame Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.97,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and put down your name and \Naddress on the form while you're in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.31,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Cash only.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.94,sign_31081_374_Yakisoba,Blue banner,0000,0000,0000,,Yakisoba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:38.94,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Four, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.95,main,Food,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 1,600 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.69,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.95,sign_31258_379_Yakisoba,Blue banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-95.95\fax-0.03\pos(114,11)\fscx116}Y{\3c&HD3A61A&}a{\3c&HBD9309&}k{\3c&HC58E13&}i{\3c&HC99315&}s{\3c&HC88B10&}o{\3c&HBC7D0A&}b{\3c&HBA7A12&}a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.07,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:55.55,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Say... have you ever been \Nsatisfied with a performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.46,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.67,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.93,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:05.47,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:11.34,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That to me, life is about \Nworking on stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:15.85,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing I can do about that, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.63,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take this to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.11,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think of my animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:32.26,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Real explosions give off a different impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:33.87,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And the way they held those chopsticks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:37.00,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You could've told me sooner! \NI didn't find out until this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.79,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was some fine acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:47.30,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from a couple \Nof actors. You know what to look for!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:55.69,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:56.56,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.26,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There were a ton of preorders for the DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.57,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And we ran out of all the \Npictures we had prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:05.91,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the reception, I feel like I'm \Nonly satisfied with 20% of what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:07.32,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:11.38,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It might've been more impressive \Nwith more long shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:13.00,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And a more detailed \Nbackground during the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:16.95,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,with the wall collapsing would've \Nadded to the sense of scale—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:21.14,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Tsubame's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.21,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.31,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're her comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:25:00.25,sign_35868_406_Illustraiton_by_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx75}Illustration by: Shoko Takahata
